    <string name="help_text">Help</string>
    <string name="help_text_content">Athelite is a fully customizable workout logger designed for any athlete.
        \n\nSimply create a template in the "Templates" section by tapping the plus button.
        Templates can be added directly to the main page, or through the calendar.
        \n\nFrom there, you can customize your template by adding custom or built in exercises.
        To create an exercise, simply change the name and the new exercise will be automatically saved.
        \n\nFinally, you can customize your exercises by adding the appropriate number of sets, reps,
        and weight.</string>

